Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.01,0:00:25.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.58,0:00:28.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.41,0:00:32.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风鸣机关本部…灰飞烟灭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.15,0:00:35.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛利亚小姐她们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.02,0:00:41.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切歌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.07,0:00:46.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作一点啊　玛利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.87,0:00:47.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.48,0:00:59.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还…活着
