Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.00,0:02:48.98,TITLE,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(593,300)\pos(930,440)}第五话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.00,0:02:48.98,TITLE,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(930,490)\fad(593,300)}虚幻战场　舍命相争
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.85,0:02:44.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,输了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.34,0:02:47.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,输得肝脑涂地体无完肤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.15,0:02:52.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴伐利亚光明会总局长终于现身了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.43,0:02:55.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚当·怀斯豪普特
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.43,0:02:56.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.30,0:03:01.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炼金术师们的Faust-Robe
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.54,0:03:03.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,短兵相接那一瞬之间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.35,0:03:08.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那股冲击就仿佛要将IGNITE的力量强行剥离
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.75,0:03:14.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那恐怕是Lapis Philosophicus 也就是贤者之石的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.45,0:03:15.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贤者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.26,0:03:17.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她确实这样说过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.69,0:03:23.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那晶体正是追求完美的炼金主旨的最终目标
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.91,0:03:29.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在其对包括疾病在内的种种不洁以燃烧的方式加以净化的特性面前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.78,0:03:35.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为IGNITE模块核心的{\fnA-OTF Kumoya Std R}Dáinsleif{\r} 其魔力对此也无能为力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.38,0:03:38.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一言以蔽之就是IGNITE的天敌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.13,0:03:43.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将身体斩断撕裂般的冲击就是强制解除造成的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.77,0:03:47.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来是杀手锏却反倒成了我们的软肋了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.58,0:03:52.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转移到东京的玛利亚小姐她们没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.81,0:03:55.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然还有待进一步精密检查
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.22,0:03:58.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们的伤势都奇迹般得并不严重
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.65,0:04:03.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.50,0:04:05.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.01,0:04:07.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定…没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.53,0:04:10.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在没有LiNKER的情况下使用Gear
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.13,0:04:13.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,IGNITE又让身体的负担雪上加霜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.05,0:04:17.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按说反噬就算达到绝唱级别也不为过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.94,0:04:18.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.41,0:04:26.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风鸣机关本部已确定立即废弃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.94,0:04:28.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立即进行撤离的准备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.53,0:04:31.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴尔韦德文件如果能成功解析的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.15,0:04:34.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知能否成为打破僵局的线索呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.38,0:04:45.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司令　镰仓召见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.65,0:04:49.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来不是被痛斥一通就能了事了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.59,0:05:03.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贤者之石的光辉压倒了IGNITE的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.81,0:05:05.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本已胜券在握
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.33,0:05:07.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.61,0:05:12.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍有差池　我们就被你烤得外焦里嫩肉汁饱满了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.52,0:05:16.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来甚至还让她们全身而退了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.96,0:05:22.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诸位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.80,0:05:24.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚当好不容易过来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.21,0:05:26.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与其闷闷不乐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.61,0:05:27.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如开心一点嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.35,0:05:31.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诸位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.69,0:05:33.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(738,666.333)}神祇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.69,0:05:33.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦好啦　缇姬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.56,0:05:37.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣日耳曼他们又不是在无理取闹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.70,0:05:42.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本打算是来帮忙同时借机秀一把来得
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.51,0:05:44.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.99,0:05:47.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是交给你们好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.37,0:05:49.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对付Symphogear
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.16,0:05:52.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总局长　移步何处
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.68,0:05:56.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(406,666.333)}神祇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.68,0:05:56.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,缇姬把观星所得的天相告诉我了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.77,0:05:57.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.86,0:06:00.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实验不是成功了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.56,0:06:04.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来就该来真的了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.93,0:06:07.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令神之力降于现世
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.40,0:06:21.72,IN_K_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}Zeios igalima raizen tron
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.50,0:06:53.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Death
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.28,0:07:09.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Shul shagana的利刃如履带般碾开一切
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.91,0:07:10.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论眼前的障碍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.54,0:07:13.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是我们的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.15,0:07:19.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无比锋利的Igalima只要认真起来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.10,0:07:21.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神挡杀神
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.12,0:07:22.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佛挡杀佛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.14,0:07:23.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一刀两断Death
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.27,0:07:32.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们两个又在胡来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.05,0:07:33.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛利亚小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.74,0:07:35.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这样不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.02,0:07:37.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都还没好利落吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.27,0:07:52.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小切
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:00.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.68,0:08:05.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,调　切歌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.72,0:08:09.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,LiNKER都没有了为什么还…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.75,0:08:15.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要是能不依靠LiNKER战斗的话　也不至于…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.44,0:08:20.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.51,0:08:21.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.26,0:08:24.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还要继续训练呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.36,0:08:27.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要不依靠LiNKER
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.03,0:08:30.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就必须提高匹配系数
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.71,0:08:32.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么能这么胡来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.46,0:08:35.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍有差池可是会死的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.03,0:08:41.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,响你不明不白就得到那么高的匹配系数怎么可能理解我们的苦衷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.40,0:08:45.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直被人像垃圾一样看待
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.90,0:08:46.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算没有死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.27,0:08:48.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也像死一样难过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.88,0:08:49.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恨不得一死了之Death
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.20,0:08:53.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让她们做下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.53,0:08:54.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛利亚小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.99,0:08:56.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为保证她们不做过头
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.08,0:08:58.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会陪她们一起训练的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.11,0:09:00.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要提高的是匹配系数啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.72,0:09:02.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉高智障系数是闹哪样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.01,0:09:06.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,LiNKER迟早会完成
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.62,0:09:13.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可时不我待　眼下局势已是刻不容缓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.05,0:09:15.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,方法不是没有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.52,0:09:21.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,补齐完成LiNKER所需缺失的最后一部分的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.70,0:09:23.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.45,0:09:24.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.99,0:09:27.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在威尔博士留下的LiNKER配方中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.06,0:09:29.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯一未能被解读的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.48,0:09:31.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.40,0:09:37.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,LiNKER是通过打通Symphogear与装者脑部哪个区域来降低负担的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.19,0:09:40.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说有菲尼和F.I.S.提供支持
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.96,0:09:43.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但能空手起家造出LiNKER的威尔博士
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.78,0:09:44.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他姑且不说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.12,0:09:47.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为生化专家而言是无可挑剔的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.05,0:09:49.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无可挑剔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.88,0:09:51.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这笑话一点都不好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.16,0:09:55.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说　这些复杂的内容都放一放
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.95,0:09:58.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直接说说那最后一部分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.42,0:10:01.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关键就在玛利亚小姐身着的{\fnArial Unicode MS\fs55}Airgetlámh{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.24,0:10:04.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,银之…我的Gear
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.35,0:10:10.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial Unicode MS\fs55}Airgetlámh{\r}有着可以操控能量矢量的特性
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.43,0:10:13.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在危急时刻时常出现的发光现象
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.08,0:10:17.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是大脑和Symphogear之间往来的电信号
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.54,0:10:19.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经{\fnArial Unicode MS\fs55}Airgetlámh{\r}的特性变得肉眼可见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.19,0:10:21.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.18,0:10:25.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,依我推测　或许还有缓和Gear带来的负担的效果
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.68,0:10:29.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛利亚小姐你们一直坚持在任务间隙中训练
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.14,0:10:33.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,匹配系数也随之逐步提高
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.46,0:10:37.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能就是受此特性影响
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.63,0:10:43.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛利亚的匹配系数在我们之中也是最高的　莫非…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.78,0:10:46.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说我们一直以来的坚持没有白费咯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.38,0:10:47.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.21,0:10:52.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我们能找出留在玛利亚小姐脑内电信号的痕迹的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.63,0:10:55.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能确定LiNKER作用的区域
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.29,0:10:57.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这要怎么做到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.16,0:11:01.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非向威尔这厮低头否则…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.59,0:11:03.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.06,0:11:06.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.33,0:11:10.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(796,666.333)}Direct Feedback System
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.33,0:11:10.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威尔博士的留下的直通回馈系统
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.93,0:11:13.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我试着用炼金术将其重造出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.48,0:11:19.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通过将意识转为电信号并介入对象大脑内部进行观测
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.64,0:11:23.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说这东西可以窥探大脑里的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.77,0:11:24.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理论上可以
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.50,0:11:29.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是人类大脑是由复杂意识构成的迷宫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.98,0:11:31.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最不幸的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.21,0:11:35.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,观测者和对象的意识会互相溶合一同成为废人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.25,0:11:36.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放手做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.92,0:11:40.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算要摸到完成LiNKER的门道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.07,0:11:42.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么能错失良机呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.74,0:11:44.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.46,0:11:46.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛利亚自暴自弃Death
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.29,0:11:47.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轮不到你们来说我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.42,0:11:53.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,观测者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.70,0:11:56.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说你也要承担这样的风险吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.70,0:11:58.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我所能做到的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.36,0:12:02.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请和我并肩作战吧　玛利亚小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.89,0:12:21.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便任由敌夷践踏蹂躏？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.34,0:12:25.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果　松代的风鸣机关本部毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.59,0:12:30.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,几乎失去了大战时保存的全部机密
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.72,0:12:34.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,引狼入室在先　应对不力于后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.32,0:12:37.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽数责无旁贷　但愿一力承担
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.60,0:12:38.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不堪入耳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.11,0:12:47.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆了然否
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.96,0:12:51.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会加快那个国土防卫议案的表决议程
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.72,0:12:54.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事急从权　即刻执行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.40,0:13:00.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实乃防人之耻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.06,0:13:04.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,徒得风鸣血脉　可哀可叹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.09,0:13:07.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾坚信　吾等尽防人之责
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.35,0:13:10.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非以血脉　乃以胸中之志
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.93,0:13:22.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.63,0:13:26.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会进到我的这里对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.30,0:13:31.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准确的说是链接到复制到虚拟空间里的玛利亚小姐的脑部构造
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.17,0:13:34.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将我和玛利亚小姐的意识共享
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.99,0:13:35.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.07,0:13:47.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小切　我知道你很担心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.82,0:13:48.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道Death
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.05,0:13:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都是心知肚明而做的决定Death
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.16,0:13:57.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巧克力鳕鱼子口味难度真的太高了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.41,0:14:00.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是我请客　别剩下哦　常识人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.05,0:14:04.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,味道很不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.51,0:14:06.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是祈愿Death
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.27,0:14:07.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能全部吃完的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.46,0:14:10.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛利亚和艾尔芙娜茵的挑战一定可以圆满成功Death
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.26,0:14:16.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,响　想什么呢　响
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.39,0:14:17.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.08,0:14:20.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,化掉了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.95,0:14:26.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听听你的心里话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.74,0:14:29.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,替你擦掉融化的冰淇淋我还是做得到的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.53,0:14:33.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以　有什么事记得要依靠我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.46,0:14:37.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢　未来　果然未来是我心中的一缕阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.55,0:14:41.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs35\fn微软简}单腿足球少年　{\c&H0000FF&}来日进行手术\N　　　　　　　　　　{\c&H000000&\fs33}NEWS　直播
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.95,0:14:39.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一条新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.32,0:14:42.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在祖国的内乱中失去了一条腿的斯提芬小朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.45,0:14:46.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为能再次踢上喜欢的足球
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.33,0:14:49.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接受安装最新义肢的手术
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.44,0:14:52.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今日从巴尔韦德共和国千里迢迢来到日本
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.03,0:14:56.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了　那孩子又能踢足球了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.35,0:14:58.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能顺风顺水就好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.77,0:15:04.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深思熟虑后的决断　不一定都是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.71,0:15:10.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岂止如此　可能一开始就没有正确的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.36,0:15:16.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备好了吧　开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.25,0:15:44.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是玛利亚小姐的脑内
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.90,0:15:46.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由记忆绘制的心像风景
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.04,0:15:55.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛利亚小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.56,0:16:03.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.12,0:16:05.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.73,0:16:10.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打今天起你们将开始进行战斗训练
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.20,0:16:14.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(816,666.333)}Receptor Children
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.20,0:16:14.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有成为菲尼容器的转世灵童
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.34,0:16:18.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就该用你们的血而不是无用的眼泪为组织出力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.27,0:16:25.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,共享意识的情况下　回忆里的体验也会波及到我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.01,0:16:40.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底在哪儿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.20,0:16:43.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和Gear连通的脑部区域
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.23,0:16:57.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快喝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.56,0:17:19.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是　关于NOISE的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.64,0:17:30.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我在这里死掉的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.89,0:17:33.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现实中的我恐怕也会不省人事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.62,0:17:53.92,IN_M_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}Seilien coffin airget-lamh tron
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.93,0:18:03.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛利亚小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.21,0:18:06.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是艾尔芙娜茵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.65,0:18:09.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把回忆随便给人看还是会害羞的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.56,0:18:13.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问　您是什么时候记忆里的哪位玛利亚小姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.14,0:18:17.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是刚和你约定了并肩战斗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.32,0:18:21.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里共享了意识的可不是只有你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.02,0:18:25.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在我自己心中大闹一番　有何不可
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.95,0:18:33.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是记忆里的玛利亚小姐　是她本人的意识
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.43,0:18:36.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突出重围
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.38,0:18:36.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.50,0:18:49.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.89,0:18:54.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.86,0:18:59.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛利亚小姐自己也不太记得的深层记忆的影像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.04,0:19:01.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深层记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.83,0:19:14.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两位情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.15,0:19:18.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生命体征已经大幅度降低到了安全线以下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.62,0:19:20.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么持续下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.86,0:19:25.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无可奈何　视情况只能一时中断观测了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.64,0:19:27.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.48,0:19:30.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在东京湾出现了Alca-NOISE的反应
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.93,0:19:33.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在出现了能使空间切断的类型之后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.11,0:19:34.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又出现了新的形态吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.12,0:19:37.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还是更加巨大的形态
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.88,0:19:39.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不能让它就这么上岛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.04,0:19:40.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.32,0:19:52.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(820,666.333)}神祇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.32,0:19:52.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想不到在歌剧院地下除了缇姬以外
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.31,0:19:55.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还藏着这么多好玩的宝贝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.35,0:19:58.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来不能继续沉默了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.28,0:20:01.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是　我们巴伐利亚光明会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.28,0:20:06.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将使用神之力将这世界引向正轨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.05,0:20:13.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是为他人着想的话　我们一定可以携手并进的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.52,0:20:16.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大义…不…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.95,0:20:18.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正义是属于我方的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.70,0:20:21.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开弓便无回头箭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.65,0:20:23.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,独闯龙潭亦在所不惜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.74,0:20:24.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不是一人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.88,0:20:28.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来是不会让你孤身一人的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.56,0:20:31.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏了圣日耳曼　我们才能站在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.72,0:20:34.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论去哪都要三个人一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.63,0:20:40.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.83,0:20:43.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\frz270\fn@微软简\fs40\pos(54.667,107.333)}已确认发生特别灾害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.83,0:20:43.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软简\fs35\3c&H0606AF&\an8}灾害信息　{\3c&H0F0F11&}东京湾沿岸地区已发布紧急避难通告
